      "date": "2014-11-04 22:55:05.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(1 comment)\n\n2 style warning(s).\nFor more details please see https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/PUB/Coding+Guidelines",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
